{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_01_03",
  "title": "実力で\nぶちのめす",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "え、ちょっと、二人ともどこ行くんですか！？\nfranさん、kanaさーん！　ど、どうすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ wait‚ where are you two going!?\nfran-san‚ kana-san~! W-what should I do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.4552150726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6485483487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "ラスベガスは治安もいいそうですし\n一人歩きをしても、昼なら問題はないでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Las Vegas has good public safety‚\nso they should be fine walking around alone during the day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6485483487,
      "endTime": 15.461860688600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.6485275269
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "スマホで連絡もつきますし\n頭が冷えたらそのうち戻ってきますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can contact them on their phones‚\nso they’ll be back once they cool down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6485275269,
      "endTime": 21.0009448052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、あの子達が戻ってくるまでは\n私もこの辺で時間を潰そうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ until they come back‚\nI’ll also kill some time around here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.174276797,
      "endTime": 27.201881186199998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.4118800163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、mihoさんがあそこで怒り出すとは\n思わなくて……その、ちょっと驚きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I didn’t expect miho-san\nto get that angry… It was a bit surprising.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4618800163,
      "endTime": 37.8510180474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "franの腑抜けっぷりに少しイラついただけです\n別に、言葉ほど腹を立ててはいませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was just a little irritated by fran’s spinelessness.\nI wasn’t as angry as I sounded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0643513997,
      "endTime": 45.265018113400004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4583511988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "才能だけはあるから、ろくでもない態度も\nこちらは我慢しているのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She does have talent‚ so I’ve been putting up with\nher terrible attitude…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4583511988,
      "endTime": 50.3762887635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "海外に来たくらいでひよるなんて、私はなんのために\n毎日性悪どもの相手をしているのかと思っただけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ she freaked out just by being abroad… I just thought\nwhat’s the point of me dealing with those jerks every day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5896222113,
      "endTime": 57.8732056616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0865387279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（それは、かなり怒ってるって言うんじゃないかな）\n（それにmihoさんもだいぶ影響を受けて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I think that means she’s pretty angry…）\n（And miho-san’s been pretty affected too…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0865387279,
      "endTime": 66.0430919963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "私は毎日、自分より上の才能を見せつけられているのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m constantly seeing talents that surpass mine every day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2297587393,
      "endTime": 70.9335711477,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.1335711477
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "自分を天才だとかのたまう人は\nそんな思いをしたこともないんでしょうね、羨ましいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "People who boast about being geniuses\nprobably have never experienced that‚ how nice for them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1335711477,
      "endTime": 77.0324671744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.2666659037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8057994523,
      "endTime": 79.7898040273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　……あの人達\nmihoさんを見て何か喋ってますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? …Those people\nare saying something while looking at miho-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0564696886,
      "endTime": 85.0042019464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.1975351748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "今、目が合いましたね……あ、こっちに歩いてくる\nここは話を聞くしかなさそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just made eye contact with them… Ah‚ they’re coming toward us.\nIt seems like we have no choice but to hear them out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1975351748,
      "endTime": 94.8501600681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "本来なら、ここはマネージャーである\n貴方が対応すべきですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ as the manager‚ you should be\nthe one handling this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0568266966,
      "endTime": 99.79749337220001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.9908267436
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "貴方の英語スキルには不安があるので、私が対応します\n……どうせ、私達のことなんて知らない人でしょうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m worried about your English skills‚ so I’ll handle it.\n…They probably don’t know us anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9908267436,
      "endTime": 109.1638268886,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9409.171476099998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.3999982197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "『これから一緒に遊びに行かないか？』……ですか\n『お断りします。仕事で来ていますので……』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Would you like to hang out with us?\" …you mean.\n\"I decline. We’re here for work…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8638268886,
      "endTime": 119.3250140605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "『本当ですよ。ショーに出演予定で……』\n……はあ、困ったわね。全く諦める気配がないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"It's true. We’re scheduled to perform in a show…\"\n…Sigh‚ this is troublesome. They show no signs of giving up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8650167563,
      "endTime": 129.8420787908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.885588359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（まずいぞ。相手はまるでmihoさんの言葉を）\n（聞いてる様子がない……。俺がなんとかしないと……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is bad. They don't seem to be listening to）\n（miho-san at all… I have to do something…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0354118762,
      "endTime": 136.9926455913,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7163.900248300024
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.1993121245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "は、ハロー！　し、……She is a……\nえ、えーと……Japanese top idol！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hello! Sh-she is a…\nUm‚ uhh… Japanese top idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1993121245,
      "endTime": 147.94582053210002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.1391538082
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャー！？　突然間に入ってきたかと思えば……\nふふっ、『アイドルって何？』と聞かれてますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager!? You suddenly jumped in and…\nFufu‚ he’s asking‚ “What's an idol?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1391538082,
      "endTime": 156.6954871593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとは何か……難しい質問ですね……\nえー……アイドルと言うのは……――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is an idol… That’s a tough question…\nUm… An idol is… --",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8821539023,
      "endTime": 164.0785257437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.265192582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_03-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "もういいです。歌とダンスを織り交ぜたパフォーマンス\nをするアーティストグループ、とでも伝えておきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine. I will tell them it’s an artist group\nthat performs songs and dances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.265192582,
      "endTime": 171.09999821969998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "amepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.7369905251
    },
    {
